import { Formik } from "formik"

initialValue = {
	login: "",
	password: "",
}

export const LoginForm = () => {

	return (
		<Formik>
			<form autoComplete='off'>
				<label htmlFor="">
					Login
					<input type="text" name="login" />
				</label>
				<label htmlFor="">
					Password
					<input type="password" login="password" />
				</label>
				<button type="submit">Send</button>
			</form>
		</Formik>

	)
}
